hashToText.xqoguQxnoeLWkiZgd66KQA==: Be careful when entering the café so that the cats do not run away. {pleading face emoji}

phrases.jsfbt: Be careful when entering the café so that the cats do not run away. {pleading face emoji}

hashToText.AZBk0HF6F8GgThvh5h0vdg==: Feel free to play with the cats and have fun. But please, respect their space and do not force them to do things they do not want, such as pulling their tails, whiskers, etc.

phrases.jsfbt: Feel free to play with the cats and have fun. But please, respect their space and do not force them to do things they do not want, such as pulling their tails, whiskers, etc.

hashToText.2fSycF0Q8vnGGrk4RLeKLg==: Try not to wake up our cats or interrupt them while they are having a snack.

phrases.jsfbt: Try not to wake up our cats or interrupt them while they are having a snack.

hashToText.0yUbdcejksJ+Iw6ARTDoag==: We encourage you to take pictures. {thumbs up emoji} But prefer to take them without a flash. Don’t forget to tag us on your Instagram {instagram account}

phrases.jsfbt: We encourage you to take pictures. {thumbs up emoji} But prefer to take them without a flash. Don’t forget to tag us on your Instagram {instagram account}

hashToText.5iTUS9k7jab+evPuLeeh7A==: Our cats have a special healthy food which you can buy from us. Human food might be dangerous for them. Please don’t feed them with your food.

phrases.jsfbt: Our cats have a special healthy food which you can buy from us. Human food might be dangerous for them. Please don’t feed them with your food.

hashToText./T78HImOiKKs6J26mVLuaQ==: Cats are very sensitive. Be careful with loud and sudden noises, which could scare them.

phrases.jsfbt: Cats are very sensitive. Be careful with loud and sudden noises, which could scare them.

hashToText.U98Bttt6bmp1PmUACerVug==: Leave your pets at home. Other pets are not allowed here.

phrases.jsfbt: Leave your pets at home. Other pets are not allowed here.

hashToText.itv8A/4Pvi/UCI1hEPlLpQ==: We are not responsible for any injuries caused by our cats - they are very playful, and they do not mean it. Pay special attention to your kids. Feel free to ask for medical aid when needed.

phrases.jsfbt: We are not responsible for any injuries caused by our cats - they are very playful, and they do not mean it. Pay special attention to your kids. Feel free to ask for medical aid when needed.

hashToText.eEHP2QM079xkRqVGx7HUlQ==: Hygiene is important. Wash your hand when playing with our cats.

phrases.jsfbt: Hygiene is important. Wash your hand when playing with our cats.

hashToText.4EOS7M5k/RGGg6oLo32EHw==: Please, follow our rules. Misbehaving guests will be asked to leave.

phrases.jsfbt: Please, follow our rules. Misbehaving guests will be asked to leave.
